<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77fe44c1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460lll–48"><num value="460lll–48">§ 460lll–48.</num><heading> Tennessee Valley Authority transfer costs</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any costs incurred by Tennessee Valley Authority associated with the transfer under this part shall be derived from funding described in section 460<i>lll</i>–49 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77fe44c2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/277/dA/s101/e/tV/s548">Pub. L. 105–277, div. A, § 101(e) [title V, § 548]</ref>, <date date="1998-10-21">Oct. 21, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2681-231">112 Stat. 2681–231</ref>, 2681–325.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
